messages.message: Sabin: Why, Vargas?{N}Why did you kill Master Duncan?{N}How could you kill your own father!?
Vargas: I'm sick of listening to your lies!{N}I've got far more than just potential!{N}Why don't you see for yourself?
Sabin: He wanted you to be his successor, not me!{N}He knew you had the most potential...
Vargas: Ah, if it isn't Sabin!
Vargas: It's true and you know it!{N}It's written in that ugly sneer across your face!
Now...{N}Get ready to join your beloved master!
Vargas: The fool snubbed me, his only son!{N}He chose you as his successor!
